skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: me who
des:
Tell Me Who can be used to get a variety of personalized thoughts, interests, messages, news and other information on friends, celebrities or businesses. As of today we are learning about the people that interest you the most, so you can request that a person is added to the Tell Me Who network. We are also reserving space for people who want their own bio to be part of the skill. Imagine your friends being able to say "Alexa, tell me who is John Smith", and getting a response, recorded by you, saying "Hi... it's John. Hit me up on twitter at jsmith1010 to find out about my latest favorite podcasts".

You can also learn about us, Cygnus Consulting, by saying "Alexa, tell me who is Cygnus Consulting".

You can learn more about this skill by going to www.cygnusconsult.com/alexa/tellmewho. You can learn more about Cygnus Consulting by going to www.cygnusconsult.com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
